\section{Results}

We calculate the dimensionless energy transfer rate between the layers separated by a distance $d$ for two different cases of the system, introduced in the previous section. The amount of transferred energy is obtained as a function of the temperature of one of the layers, $t_2$ for fixed $t_1$.

